VOID ID(main) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
INT ID(x) SEMICOLON
ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("x=") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(x) ASSIGN ID(get_i) LPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
IF LPAREN ID(x) LT CT_INT(0) RPAREN ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("negative") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ELSE ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("positive") RPAREN SEMICOLON
RBRACE
